cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper discusses the development of a benchmark for deep learning-based recommendation models, which falls under the category of machine learning and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper discusses the use of deep learning, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely sub-category. Finally, since the paper discusses the use of data sets, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible sub-category as well.
